snippet.title: Please Care Over Stories {PCOS} Gameplay
snippet.description:
Please Care Over Stories is a game based on personal experience with the chronic condition of Poly-cystic Ovary Syndrome. 

Feel free to give it a play on my itch.io:
https://oracle-animosity.itch.io/please-care-over-stories

SOCIAL MEDIA:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/OracleAnimosity
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/oracleanimosity/

Website: https://oracleanimosity.wixsite.com/professional
Blog: https://oracleanimosity.wordpress.com/
